<p><strong>19. Ending your relationship with Mint.com</strong></p>

<p>This Agreement will continue to apply until terminated by either you or Intuit (or any Intuit affiliate/subsidiary) as set out below. If you want to terminate this legal agreement for the Services, you may do so as follows:</p>

<p>To close your account, please use the directions below:</p>

<p>For users who have accounts added in Mint:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Login to your Mint.com account via the Mint website.</li>
	<li>Go to “Settings”.</li>
	<li>Click the “Delete your Mint account” option under “Sign In &amp; Security”.</li>
	<li>Click “YES, delete my Mint Account” and you will be prompted to enter your password.</li>
	<li>Click “Delete Account” to delete your account.</li>
	<li>Your account will be closed and your ability to log in deactivated immediately. Your Mint.com account data will be removed as explained in our Privacy Statement and we will send you a confirmation via email.</li>
</ul>

<p>For users who have no accounts added in Mint:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Login to your Mint.com account via the Mint website.</li>
	<li>Scroll to the bottom of the main page and click the link that says "Delete your Mint account "(If you recently deleted your bank accounts, please logout and then log back in once more to view the “Delete your Mint account” link on the main page).</li>
	<li>A pop up box will appear, select “YES, delete my Mint Account” and you will be prompted to enter your password.</li>
	<li>Click “Delete Account” to delete your account.</li>
	<li>Click “Delete Account” to delete your account.</li>
	<li>Your account will be closed and your ability to log in deactivated immediately. Your Mint.com account data will be removed as explained in our Privacy Statement and we will send you a confirmation via email.</li>
</ul>

<p>To remove Mint from your mobile devices, delete the Mobile App. However, deleting the app will not delete your Mint account, it will only delete the data from the device. Therefore, in order to close your account for the Mint Service, login to Mint.com via the web and follow the instructions above.</p>

